English.Name: Nova Pyrotechnica

Localization.Name: Viper III-G Missile
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Nova Pyrotechnica 
Tracking Signal: Infrared 
Size: 3  

Nova has worked hard to insure that their infrared tracking Viper strike missile lives up to its name by delivering agile and lethal attacks against hostile targets. Note: This missile may only be launched by ground vehicles.
